    <p class="gd-lede">Heliskiing takes you into wild, unpatrolled mountains, so it can never be made risk-free — but it can be managed to an exceptionally high standard. This chapter explains, honestly, how that is done on Iceland's <a href="/heliskiing-guide/troll-peninsula-terrain">Troll Peninsula</a>: the IFMGA guides who make every terrain decision, the daily avalanche assessment, the safety kit you carry, the rescue-capable helicopter, and the insurance you should arrange before you travel with <a href="/packages">Heliski Travel</a>.</p>
